Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:11.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}獨個兒寂寞難耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:18.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}於是牽住了夥伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:24.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}這樣的話將永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:29.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年無憂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:36.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論如何都想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:42.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夥伴們曾牽在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:49.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已變得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:53.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一個個漸漸離去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:02:00.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}向著那甦醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:09.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}邁開腳步毅然前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:18.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}彷彿節日的喧囂過後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:24.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只留下了寂寞
